lori (0.14.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add Modbus Connector
  * Add InfluxDB v2 Connector
  * Add cycletime configuration to RevPi connector
  * Implement virtual dummy generator
  * Implement short waiting for listeners before logging
  * Implement generic analog IO converters
  * Fix reconnecting connectors
  * Fix float from str conversion
  * Fix recursive registrator inclusion
  * Fix default pandas hashing for consecutive NaN values
  * Fix SQL hashing for large BLOB types
  * Fix SQL database bool column creation
  * Fix RevPi Connector timestamp flooring

